def make_cat_total_area(total_area):
    if 0 <= total_area < 20:
        return '0-20'
    elif 20 <= total_area < 40:
        return '20-40'
    elif 40 <= total_area < 60:
        return '40-60'
    elif 60 <= total_area < 80:
        return '60-80'
    elif 80 <= total_area < 100:
        return '80-100'
    else:
        return ' 100'
